          "Common mistakes include ignoring joist direction, forgetting board gaps, assuming all boards are perfect, undercounting fasteners, using indoor hardware outdoors, setting footings above frost depth, attaching ledgers incorrectly, and forgetting stairs or railings. A free deck calculator online gives instant results and works on mobile and desktop, but a safe deck still requires careful structural review. Use the estimate to plan cost, then verify spans, connections, and permit requirements before building.",
